PERMITTED USE (THE ONLY THINGS YOU MAY LEGALLY DO)
================================================================================

Subject to the restrictions above, you may:

- Clone and use the repository for personal educational study on your own
  legally owned vehicles and devices.
- Run the Python generator scripts to produce templates and playlists for
  your own use.
- Capture signals from hardware you own using the documented techniques.
- Use the capture_helper.py and rolljam_prep.py scripts on your own .sub files.
- Modify the Python scripts and documentation for your personal research
  (you must keep all original legal disclaimers and Kelly commentary intact).
- Contribute verified captures + metadata from hardware you own back to the
  project via proper channels (only data you personally captured and verified
  on your own property).

All other uses — including but not limited to commercial use, redistribution
of capture files from unknown sources, or any activity that violates the
restrictions section — are unlicensed and prohibited.

